{"id":"6041","name":"happy-hour-dont-drink-the-________","title":"Happy Hour: Don&#x2019;t Drink The ________","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-11-15T17:30:00-06:00","tags":["bells bend","belmont university","brentwood","extreme makeover","jack may","law school","lighthouse christian school","may town center","parks &amp; recreation","rutherford county jail"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you are new here, you might want to <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to the RSS feed</strong></a> for updates on this topic.<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/blueshoe/5173331802/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4148/5173331802_18ec073bc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\"></a></p><ul><li>The Rutherford County jail is slashing more than $100K from their food budget by, uh, not serving inmates Kool-Aid. Or coffee, or salt and pepper, or jelly. But the point here is that they were previously spending $26,000 on <em>Kool-Aid</em>. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/money/25798423/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Brentwood bought a 320-acre plot of land for $10 million to build a park, which will increase their park lands by 50%. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/25798247/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Belmont started blasting holes in the ground for their fancy new law school and the&#xA0;dynamiting&#xA0;is scheduled to continue through February. So if you live over there,&#xA0;Godspeed. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101115/NEWS01/101115024/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>The controversial Bells Bend debate may be back at the forefront now that developer Jack May says he&#x2019;d like to revive his May Town Center plans in a much smaller form. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101115/NEWS01/101115049/May+Town+Center+developer+says+he+s+reviving+plan+in+smaller+form\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>In case you missed the big reveal of Lighthouse Christian School on <em>Extreme Makeover</em> yesterday, here is a nice photo gallery of the new digs. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/gallery?Avis=DN&amp;Dato=20101115&amp;Kategori=NEWS01&amp;Lopenr=11150801&amp;Ref=PH\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_self\">Tennessean</a>]</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/blueshoe/5173331802/in/pool-715021@N